📈 Sales Forecasting

📌 Objective
Forecast future sales using historical sales data with time-series analysis.

📊 Dataset
    - Features: Date, Sales
    - Target: Future Sales

🔧 Steps Taken
    - Checked for missing values and trends
    - Performed data visualization (line plots, seasonal patterns)
    - Applied Time Series models (ARIMA, Moving Average, Linear Regression on trends)
    - Evaluated forecast accuracy using RMSE/MAE

🏆 Results
    - Clear upward/downward sales trends detected
    - ARIMA model produced the most reliable forecasts



